{"tid":2377604,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"到底係未我管得太多","createTime":"2021-01-23T17:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T18:46:32.000Z","uid":153877,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d3bb3977bb5ce5c7bb19de7ada6ffa44ef10c4","tid":2377604,"uid":153877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:53:38.000Z","msg":"最近依幾日，日日都見到條仔開住tg成日覆人機。我都無理到事關我對佢100%信任。 <br />\n但係琴日我好奇問下咩谷嚟，咁多水吹。 之後佢話女嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁無咩嘢嘅，人唔係男就女。問點識佢話係連登留tg等人搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後佢都俾我睇佢同啲女傾過啲咩。 <br />\n睇到原來依幾日有兩三條女搵過佢（得一條仔）<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地起佢底問佢女朋友呢？ 佢就話佢開po入面條女已經散咗。 問佢做咩唔話人知佢而家有女，佢就話人地都無問佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問佢做乜擺低tg等人搵，佢話佢悶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英國lockdown 我知日日係屋企悶淨係對住我好撚悶，唔係上堂就打機。但我唔明攞低埋tg日傾夜傾咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知佢真係純傾，但我心入面有條刺。<br />\n今次已經係第二次<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實要搵人傾係連登都傾到，使乜留tg。 定已經對厭咗我<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947e90f6f257bb422150eead38390de3bcae13d6","tid":2377604,"uid":302117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"問得出自己都知啦"},{"pid":"8b4efacad07f10534eb9b3541efff5baeda883cf","tid":2377604,"uid":153877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"947e90f6f257bb422150eead38390de3bcae13d6","tid":2377604,"uid":302117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:55:53.000Z","msg":"問得出自己都知啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T17:58:47.000Z","msg":"但有女唔係應該避嫌，唔主動去識女嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身識落/真實朋友就無問題姐"},{"pid":"951b5c0e9c22cce93b8a0756bd60dd80b176d7f7","tid":2377604,"uid":311872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score